C - CREATE
    - write new data to our database
    (e.g CREATE TABLE, inserting rows, adding columns)
R - READ
    - reveals, shows us the data in our database, access our data
    (e.g SELECT, GROUP BY, ORDER BY)
U - UPDATE
    - edits or changes existing data
    (e.g ALTER TABLE, CHANGE COLUMN, UPDATE)
D - DESTROY
    - deletes data, erases data from our database.... PERMANENTLY
    (e.g DROP TABLE, DESTROY)